WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.000
Hello, welcome to fun trick training session.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.000
Today we'll learn how to teach your dog to give a high-five.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
High-five is more than just a trick; it strengthens the bond with your pet.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.000
First, prepare some treats and start with your dog in a sitting position.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Hold your palm flat at your dog's face level.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:33.000
When they touch it with their paw out of curiosity, immediately say "high-five" and give a treat.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Through repetition, they'll learn to respond just to the "high-five" command.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Be patient and give lots of praise when they succeed.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.000
With consistent practice, they'll soon show off an impressive high-five.